        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Nicotine</ENAMEX> and Pain
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Nicotine</ENAMEX>'s salutary effects in <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> with neurodegenerative and mental <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">disorders</ENAMEX> have
        been studied a lot and are fairly well known. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Two much</NUMEX> newer topics of academic research
        are <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">nicotine</ENAMEX>'s potential for pain relief and for treating obesity.Nicotine itself has
