        against pain, with the aim of developing more selective <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">drugs</ENAMEX>.
        Meanwhile, nicotine is also being investigated as an analgesic in <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">humans</ENAMEX>. For example,
