        scores of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">eight</NUMEX> out of a possible <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">ten</NUMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">the first hour</TIMEX> after surgery. <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Women</ENAMEX> who got
        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">nicotine</ENAMEX> averaged a pain score of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">five</NUMEX>. Despite the small sample size, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Flood</ENAMEX> says, the
