        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Nicotine</ENAMEX>'s Future
        Developing new <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">drugs</ENAMEX> that selectively target specific subtypes of <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">nicotine receptors</ENAMEX> is
